Tennis Ball Collecting Robot
<!-- Content -->
<div class="main">
  <div class="title">Tennis Ball Collecting Mobile Robot</div>

  <div class="gallery">
    <div>
      <div class="heading">What did we build?</div>

      <p>
        We set out to design and construct a mobile robot which collects tennis balls inside a tennis court quadrant and deposits them in a cardboard box. The
        project was subject to time, cost and materials constraints, prompting us to make several difficult tradeoffs to ensure reliable operation during the
        final demonstration for the project unit.
      </p>
    </div>

